<span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-24_">The keystone of leadership: Unpacking manager induction in adult social care</span></h2><p class="sc-fIosxK hdNOer pf-25_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-27_">In the dynamic and demanding realm of adult social care, the role of a manager transcends beyond mere administration; it is about fostering a culture of compassion, efficiency, and excellence. The induction of managers in this sector, therefore, is not just a formality but a critical foundation for the success of the organisation and the well-being of its clients.<br><br>This blog delves into the significance, components, and impacts of a well-structured manager induction program in the adult social care sector.
