</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gUQvok dVgjzi pf-48_"><b>Leadership skills development</b> - Training focuses on honing essential leadership and management skills, vital for guiding teams and making impactful decisions.

</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gUQvok dVgjzi pf-50_"><b>Legal and regulatory compliance</b> - Managers gain a comprehensive understanding of the legal and regulatory environment, including adherence to standards set by bodies like the Care Quality Commission (CQC).
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gUQvok dVgjzi pf-52_"><b>Resource management</b> - Developing skills in managing budgets, resources, and staff scheduling to optimise operational efficiency.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gUQvok dVgjzi pf-54_"><b>Communication and relationship building</b> - Cultivating strong communication skills for effective team management and stakeholder engagement.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gUQvok dVgjzi pf-56_"><b>Strategic planning and implementation</b> - Training in setting and achieving strategic organisational goals.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gUQvok dVgjzi pf-58_"><b>Risk management and problem-solving</b> - Enhancing abilities to identify, assess, and manage risks, and cultivating problem-solving capabilities.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gUQvok dVgjzi pf-60_"><b>Personal development planning</b> - Guidance on continuous personal and professional growth, setting and achieving career milestones.
</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-dFtzxp icSyEj pf-62_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cLpAjG dTtSfA pf-64_">Importance of manager induction
