</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gUQvok dVgjzi pf-72_"><b>Promotes consistency and quality of care</b> - Well-trained managers uphold and enforce care standards, ensuring uniformity and excellence across the organisation.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gUQvok dVgjzi pf-74_"><b>Enhances compliance and risk management</b> - A deep understanding of legal and regulatory frameworks aids in maintaining compliance and mitigating risks, a critical aspect in the regulated social care sector.
