</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gUQvok dVgjzi pf-78_"><b>Supports staff retention and development</b> - Effective managers are instrumental in retaining staff and fostering their development, creating a nurturing and progressive work environment.
